# Figma frontend bundle — reintroduced as the M7 local demo surface
# (owner-approved 2026-05-21; see CODING_STANDARDS §3 deviations). Kept
# gitignored on purpose: it is a localhost demo UI over the M6 API, not a
# shipped F1-F5 surface. The Python prototype remains the version-controlled
# product. DeepfakeDetectionDemo.tsx (getDisplayMedia -> /detect) and
# CryptoSignatureDemo.tsx (/sign + /verify) are the M7 real-backend demo flows.
